There are basically 3 levels of horses.<br>
<br>
#1: Jboots speed.. (travelers boots are cheaper or camp jboots in oot or sro)<br>
<br>
#2: Faster then jboots slower then sow<br>
<br>
#3: Faster then sow slower then bard song.<br>
<br>
The only horse which is 'viable' or deamed 'worthwhile' is horse #3. But Steeltoe, I can afford to buy Horse #2 NOW! Well my adivse to you would be to save your money a bit longer and step up to horse #3 or dont waste your money... but thats up to you.<br>
